    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Parents Should Give Children Right Direction</strong>&mdash;With us as parents and as Christians it rests to give our children right direction. They are to be carefully, wisely, tenderly guided into paths of Christlike ministry. We are under sacred covenant with God to rear our children for His service. To surround them with such influences as shall lead them to choose a life of service, and to give them the training needed, is our first duty.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">1<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"MH 396.1\" data-link=\"135.2004\">The Ministry of Healing, 396</span>.</span></a></sup>",
