    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>God Wants Children as Little Missionaries</strong>&mdash;God wants every child of tender age to be His child, to be adopted into His family. Young though they may be, the youth may be members of the household of faith and have a most precious experience.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">7<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"Lt 104, 1897\" data-link=\"14062.6820001\">Letter 104, 1897</span>.</span></a></sup>",
