    "content": "Let parents teach their little ones the truth as it is in Jesus. The children in their simplicity will repeat to their associates that which they have learned.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">10<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"Ms 19, 1900\" data-link=\"14065.10243001\">Manuscript 19, 1900</span>.</span></a></sup>",
