    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Let Christian Families Enter Dark Counties</strong> .&mdash;God calls for Christian families to go into communities that are in darkness and error, and work wisely and perseveringly for the Master. To answer this call requires self-sacrifice. While many are waiting to have every obstacle removed, souls are dying without hope and without God in the world. Many, very many, for the sake of worldly advantage, for the sake of acquiring scientific knowledge, will venture into pestilential regions and endure hardship and privation. Where are those who are willing to do this for the sake of telling others of the Saviour? Where are the men and women who will move <span class=\"page-break\" data-page=\"489\"></span> into regions that are in need of the gospel, that they may point those in darkness to the Redeemer?<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">13<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"9T 33.1\" data-link=\"115.172\">Testimonies for the Church 9:33</span>.</span></a></sup>",
