    "content": "<strong>Children Will Work When Others Cannot</strong>&mdash;When heavenly intelligences see that men are no longer permitted to present the truth, the Spirit of God will come upon the children, and they will do a work in the proclamation of the truth which the older workers cannot do because their way will be hedged up.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">15<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"6T 202.2\" data-link=\"118.1081\">Ibid., 203</span>.</span></a></sup>",
